window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Is Sofia chasing her past, or is her past chasing her?</p> <p>Follow Sofia as she grows and tries to use her newfound strength to escape from the clutches of the mysterious God who set her on her path.</p> <p>She will meet more people, discover more about the strange world she lives in, cause more catastrophic explosion, and, most importantly, cherish the new skeletons she meets along the way.</p>"; 
